		"name": "Regression - Run 20 Tests (UI 6-15, API 26-35), Reports & Artifacts",
		"description": "Run all 20 tests by testCaseIds (UI: 6-15, API: 26-35) with optional scheduledTime, monitor status, generate reports, and download HTML/CSV/JUnit and artifacts.",
